South Pacific Sea Level na Climate Monitoring Project (SPSLCMP) bụ ọrụ gọọmentị Australia malitere
Ebumnuche bụ isi nkè ọrụ ahụ bụ inye ihe ndekọ ziri ezi, ogologo ógè nke ọdịiche nke oke osimiri na Pacific na South Pacific.
E nwèrè agwaetiti irí na anọ nke Pacific na-ekere òkè na ọrụ nlekota oke osimiri na ihu igwe
